    "id": "silver-01-silver-slot-cleansed-c0",
    "type": "markdown",
    "source": "# Silver Layer: Slot Machine Data Cleansing\n\nThis notebook transforms Bronze slot telemetry data into cleansed Silver layer tables.\n\n## Transformations Applied:\n- Schema enforcement and type casting\n- Null handling and default values\n- Data quality validation and scoring\n- Derived KPIs: net_win, hold_percentage, is_jackpot, is_game_play, event_day_of_week\n- Deduplication (deterministic, latest record wins)\n- Standardization of codes and formats\n- Future-dated event rejection\n- Invalid denomination default-replace (0.01)"
