    "type": "markdown",
    "source": "# Silver Layer: Compliance Validated\n\nThis notebook validates compliance filings against regulatory requirements.\n\n## Validations:\n- CTR amount threshold verification\n- SAR filing completeness\n- W-2G jackpot threshold validation\n- Filing deadline compliance"
